cceptance Criteria:**\n- `Context(\"CodeInterpreter Creation\", func() { ... })` context block\n- `It(\"should create CodeInterpreter successfully\")` verifies creation succeeds\n- `It(\"should apply default values\")` verifies defaults are applied\n- `It(\"should become ready\")` verifies Ready status becomes true\n- Tests verify Name and Namespace are set correctly\n- Tests verify default values are applied\n- Tests verify status transitions to Ready\n- All tests have appropriate timeouts\n- `go test ./test/e2e/codeinterpreter/ -run CodeInterpreterCreation` passes with valid deployment\n\n**Dependencies:** T-3.1  \n**Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 Implement CodeInterpreter Execution Tests\n\n**Task ID:** T-3.3  \n**Description:** Implement tests for CodeInterpreter code execution workflows\n\n**File:** `test/e2e/codeinterpreter/execution_test.go`\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- `Context(\"Code Execution\", func() { ... })` context block\n- `BeforeEach` creates CodeInterpreter and waits for ready\n- `It(\"should execute Python code successfully\")` verifies Python code runs and returns output\n- `It(\"should handle syntax errors\")` verifies syntax errors are reported\n- `It(\"should handle runtime errors\")` verifies runtime errors are reported\n- `It(\"should preserve state between executions\")` verifies variable persistence\n- Tests verify execution output\n- Tests verify error messages\n- Tests have appropriate timeouts\n- `go test ./test/e2e/codeinterpreter/ -run CodeExecution` passes with valid deployment\n\n**Dependencies:** T-3.2  \n**Estimated Time:** 2.5 hours\n\n---\n\n### 3.4 Implement CodeInterpreter File Operations Tests\n\n**Task ID:** T-3.4  \n**Description:** Implement tests for CodeInterpreter file upload/download workflows\n\n**File:** `test/e2e/codeinterpreter/file_operations_test.go`\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- `Context(\"File Operations\", func() { ... })` context block\n- `BeforeEach` creates CodeInterpreter and waits for read