ecute pack -> build -> publish -> invoke workflow\")` verifies complete workflow\n- Workflow steps:\n  1. Create AgentRuntime\n  2. Wait for ready\n  3. Create session\n  4. Invoke session multiple times\n  5. Verify results\n  6. Clean up\n- Tests verify each step succeeds\n- Tests verify workflow completes successfully\n- Tests have appropriate timeouts (15 minutes)\n- `go test ./test/e2e/integration/ -run WorkflowIntegration` passes with valid deployment\n\n**Dependencies:** T-2.6, T-3.5  \n**Estimated Time:** 3 hours\n\n---\n\n### 4.2 Implement Routing Integration Tests\n\n**Task ID:** T-4.2  \n**Description:** Implement tests for router to workload-manager integration\n\n**File:** `test/e2e/integration/routing_test.go`\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- `Describe(\"Routing Integration\", func() { ... })` describe block\n- `BeforeSuite` initializes framework and waits for AgentCube to be ready\n- `It(\"should route requests to workload-manager correctly\")` verifies routing\n- `It(\"should handle route updates\")` verifies dynamic route changes\n- `It(\"should handle route failures gracefully\")` verifies fallback behavior\n- Tests create session via workload-manager\n- Tests invoke via router\n- Tests verify requests reach correct endpoint\n- Tests verify error handling\n- Tests have appropriate timeouts\n- `go test ./test/e2e/integration/ -run RoutingIntegration` passes with valid deployment\n\n**Dependencies:** T-4.1  \n**Estimated Time:** 2.5 hours\n\n---\n\n### 4.3 Implement Session Management Tests\n\n**Task ID:** T-4.3  \n**Description:** Implement tests for session lifecycle across components\n\n**File:** `test/e2e/integration/session_management_test.go`\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- `Describe(\"Session Management Integration\", func() { ... })` describe block\n- `BeforeSuite` initializes framework and waits for AgentCube to be ready\n- `It(\"should manage session across restarts\")` verifies session survives restart\n- `It(\"should handle session isolation